metadata.description: Official PixelMap Wrapped Tile.  Created in 2016, PixelMap is considered the second oldest NFT, the oldest verified collection on OpenSea, and provides the ability to create, display, and immortalize artwork directly on the blockchain.  All tiles can be viewed at https://pixelmap.io, and customized by the owner (image and URL are stored on-chain in the OG contract.  PixelMap was launched on November 17, 2016 - https://etherscan.io/address/0x015a06a433353f8db634df4eddf0c109882a15ab.  For more information, visit the Discord, at https://discord.pixelmap.io
metadata.name: Tile #1
